1
00:00:50,439 --> 00:00:50,920
Lin Hao,

2
00:00:53,200 --> 00:00:54,039
did you break up with me

3
00:00:55,200 --> 00:00:56,399
because of Lan Xiaochuan?

4
00:01:00,439 --> 00:01:00,960
No.

5
00:01:01,679 --> 00:01:02,719
Then why?

6
00:01:03,159 --> 00:01:03,759
Lin Hao,

7
00:01:13,719 --> 00:01:14,760
even if it's fake,

8
00:01:15,519 --> 00:01:16,480
you still rushed in.

9
00:02:10,680 --> 00:02:13,400
Groom, please put the ring on the bride's finger.

10
00:02:14,039 --> 00:02:16,560
Remember the temperature of her fingertips at this moment.

11
00:02:17,080 --> 00:02:19,039
In the days to come,

12
00:02:19,319 --> 00:02:21,360
protect her light in her eyes

13
00:02:21,560 --> 00:02:23,039
as you protect this ring.

14
00:02:24,960 --> 00:02:27,800
And the bride, please put the ring on the groom's finger.

15
00:02:29,280 --> 00:02:32,280
Hold his hand through thick and thin,

16
00:02:32,960 --> 00:02:35,759
as if holding the whole world's stability.

17
00:02:39,199 --> 00:02:41,520
Groom, you may now kiss the bride.

18
00:02:57,199 --> 00:02:57,719
Auntie,

19
00:02:58,280 --> 00:03:00,240
shall we call it a day?

20
00:03:03,879 --> 00:03:04,319
Okay.

21
00:03:04,479 --> 00:03:05,120
Let's call it a day.

22
00:03:06,159 --> 00:03:07,319
His speech

23
00:03:07,439 --> 00:03:08,879
is too pretentious.

24
00:03:09,240 --> 00:03:10,159
I don't like it.

25
00:03:10,319 --> 00:03:11,080
I need to make some changes.

26
00:03:13,919 --> 00:03:14,479
Auntie,

27
00:03:15,319 --> 00:03:16,599
why don't you rehearse with my dad?

28
00:03:16,680 --> 00:03:18,000
After all, you two are getting married, right?

29
00:03:18,319 --> 00:03:19,199
That won't do.

30
00:03:19,319 --> 00:03:20,879
Your dad and I both believe in old customs.

31
00:03:21,120 --> 00:03:22,919
We can't meet before the wedding.

32
00:03:23,360 --> 00:03:24,439
During this time,

33
00:03:24,599 --> 00:03:26,520
you two will be our little pigeons.

34
00:03:27,159 --> 00:03:28,319
We two...

35
00:03:30,439 --> 00:03:31,000
It's the ninth.

36
00:03:31,680 --> 00:03:32,439
What ninth?

37
00:03:32,840 --> 00:03:33,719
What number nine?

38
00:03:35,960 --> 00:03:36,639
Number nine.

39
00:03:36,719 --> 00:03:38,759
I'll go get my dad's suit.

40
00:03:40,280 --> 00:03:40,840
What are you doing?

41
00:03:42,400 --> 00:03:43,639
Isn't it the ninth today?

42
00:03:44,080 --> 00:03:44,759
Today?

43
00:03:46,759 --> 00:03:47,800
I'll go now.

44
00:03:49,280 --> 00:03:50,080
Yunfei, see him off.

45
00:03:50,199 --> 00:03:50,599
No need.

46
00:03:50,680 --> 00:03:51,520
Okay, no need.

47
00:03:54,639 --> 00:03:56,680
Your dad's wedding clothes are pretty nice.

48
00:03:57,039 --> 00:03:58,120
It must be expensive.

49
00:04:03,960 --> 00:04:05,000
It's okay. Let's go.

50
00:04:41,199 --> 00:04:41,800
Hello.

51
00:04:43,120 --> 00:04:43,839
Are you done?

52
00:04:45,600 --> 00:04:46,480
What do you want to do?

53
00:04:47,040 --> 00:04:47,680
Xiaochuan,

54
00:04:48,199 --> 00:04:49,399
I'm in the wedding dress store.

55
00:04:49,680 --> 00:04:51,040
Look at this mess.

56
00:04:51,480 --> 00:04:52,639
Your dad is getting married,

57
00:04:52,879 --> 00:04:53,920
but he didn't tell me.

58
00:04:54,000 --> 00:04:54,959
Did you get the money

59
00:04:55,000 --> 00:04:56,199
for this month?

60
00:04:57,199 --> 00:04:58,199
Get out of here.

61
00:04:59,000 --> 00:05:00,040
I got the money,

62
00:05:00,319 --> 00:05:01,279
but it's not enough.

63
00:05:01,879 --> 00:05:02,480
Xiaochuan,

64
00:05:02,920 --> 00:05:04,639
is that all the money for a life?

65
00:05:05,079 --> 00:05:06,279
Shame on you!

66
00:05:14,800 --> 00:05:15,600
How do you feel?

67
00:05:16,040 --> 00:05:17,240
My arm has been numb

68
00:05:17,240 --> 00:05:18,519
since I got pregnant.

69
00:05:19,040 --> 00:05:20,639
If you weren't here for acupuncture,

70
00:05:21,040 --> 00:05:22,560
no one could cure it.

71
00:05:23,040 --> 00:05:24,720
Thank you, Dr. Xiaochuan.

72
00:05:25,000 --> 00:05:25,519
You're welcome.

73
00:05:26,199 --> 00:05:26,959
It's unnecessary.

74
00:05:28,000 --> 00:05:28,680
Liu, Liu.

75
00:05:28,959 --> 00:05:30,399
She is my niece.

76
00:05:30,519 --> 00:05:32,439
You can treat her as your niece.

77
00:05:32,879 --> 00:05:33,639
You don't have to be polite.

78
00:05:33,920 --> 00:05:34,759
Next time,

79
00:05:35,040 --> 00:05:35,879
I'll give you a discount.

80
00:05:44,680 --> 00:05:45,519
What are you doing?

81
00:05:45,639 --> 00:05:46,319
You killed my baby.

82
00:05:46,800 --> 00:05:47,439
You must pay for it.

83
00:05:48,759 --> 00:05:49,160
Liu.

84
00:05:49,240 --> 00:05:49,759
This...

85
00:05:49,879 --> 00:05:50,639
What's going on?

86
00:05:50,839 --> 00:05:52,279
You shameless quack!

87
00:05:52,519 --> 00:05:53,480
You fraud!

88
00:05:53,639 --> 00:05:54,839
My wife had a miscarriage

89
00:05:54,959 --> 00:05:56,079
after getting acupuncture from you!

90
00:05:56,319 --> 00:05:57,040
You owe me my son's life!

91
00:05:57,199 --> 00:05:57,959
You murderer!

92
00:05:58,519 --> 00:05:58,920
What...

93
00:06:00,160 --> 00:06:00,560
What...

94
00:06:01,399 --> 00:06:02,040
Impossible!

95
00:06:02,240 --> 00:06:03,480
Impossible!

96
00:06:03,560 --> 00:06:04,240
You...

97
00:06:04,680 --> 00:06:05,399
Liu, Liu,

98
00:06:05,560 --> 00:06:06,120
just say it.

99
00:06:06,120 --> 00:06:07,319
-I'll beat you to death today. -Just say it.

100
00:06:07,319 --> 00:06:07,720
Don't beat me, don't beat me.

101
00:06:07,720 --> 00:06:09,000
My son is dead, don't beat me.

102
00:06:09,240 --> 00:06:09,800
Don't beat me.

103
00:06:20,800 --> 00:06:22,160
You are really rich.

104
00:06:23,319 --> 00:06:24,120
Okay, okay, okay.

105
00:06:24,199 --> 00:06:26,079
Lan Jianhua,

106
00:06:26,399 --> 00:06:28,040
you are really rich.

107
00:06:28,160 --> 00:06:28,720
Don't move.

108
00:06:30,680 --> 00:06:31,319
Xiaochuan,

109
00:06:32,879 --> 00:06:34,000
Why didn't you tell me

110
00:06:34,279 --> 00:06:35,639
your dad got married?

111
00:06:36,639 --> 00:06:38,639
Lan Jianhua is such a shameless jerk.

112
00:06:39,040 --> 00:06:40,079
He killed my sister,

113
00:06:40,319 --> 00:06:41,519
and now he's gonna kill someone else?

114
00:06:41,879 --> 00:06:42,240
Well,

115
00:06:42,600 --> 00:06:43,680
he has money

116
00:06:43,879 --> 00:06:44,759
to hold a wedding,

117
00:06:45,199 --> 00:06:45,800
but he doesn't have money

118
00:06:45,800 --> 00:06:47,399
to help his own brother-in-law?

119
00:06:47,839 --> 00:06:48,680
My dad earned the money

120
00:06:48,759 --> 00:06:50,120
for his wedding himself.

121
00:06:50,639 --> 00:06:51,600
What does it have to do with you?

122
00:06:52,040 --> 00:06:53,600
He has supported you for years.

123
00:06:53,959 --> 00:06:55,480
I also send you money every now and then.

124
00:06:56,079 --> 00:06:57,000
Isn't that enough?

125
00:06:57,759 --> 00:06:58,319
Come on,

126
00:06:58,399 --> 00:07:00,000
why are you so rude?

127
00:07:01,160 --> 00:07:02,600
Honestly, the money you gave

128
00:07:02,680 --> 00:07:03,639
wasn't for me.

129
00:07:03,959 --> 00:07:05,600
It was all for the victim.

130
00:07:06,000 --> 00:07:06,480
Over the years,

131
00:07:06,639 --> 00:07:07,680
if I hadn't mediated,

132
00:07:07,839 --> 00:07:08,600
you would have been ruined.

133
00:07:10,399 --> 00:07:11,920
You're my niece.

134
00:07:12,240 --> 00:07:13,199
If I don't care about you,

135
00:07:14,199 --> 00:07:14,920
who will?

136
00:07:15,319 --> 00:07:16,480
Don't use this to shut me up.

137
00:07:17,079 --> 00:07:18,199
After that incident,

138
00:07:18,759 --> 00:07:20,600
you've been stopping me from seeing that pregnant woman.

139
00:07:21,720 --> 00:07:23,399
If you're so sure, let me ask her face to face.

140
00:07:23,720 --> 00:07:24,920
You want to see them?

141
00:07:26,600 --> 00:07:27,920
You still want to see them?

142
00:07:28,079 --> 00:07:29,319
She miscarried.

143
00:07:29,480 --> 00:07:31,079
She hates you so much.

144
00:07:31,360 --> 00:07:32,879
She's tormented by her in-laws every day.

145
00:07:32,959 --> 00:07:34,879
You know how hard her life is now?

146
00:07:35,040 --> 00:07:36,839
She just wants some compensation.

147
00:07:37,439 --> 00:07:38,199
What do you want

148
00:07:38,519 --> 00:07:39,079
to meet her for?

149
00:07:39,639 --> 00:07:40,439
To make things worse?

150
00:07:41,000 --> 00:07:42,680
There are proper procedures for compensation.

151
00:07:43,240 --> 00:07:44,480
Why would she need you to pass messages?

152
00:07:45,040 --> 00:07:45,839
Did you

153
00:07:46,519 --> 00:07:47,680
give her the money?

154
00:07:47,959 --> 00:07:49,079
Who knows, right?

155
00:07:51,959 --> 00:07:52,600
She said

156
00:07:53,439 --> 00:07:55,759
if she gets 500,000 within three days,

157
00:07:55,879 --> 00:07:57,160
and then it's done.

158
00:07:57,800 --> 00:07:58,959
500,000?

159
00:07:59,879 --> 00:08:01,120
Why don't you just rob someone?

160
00:08:01,319 --> 00:08:02,879
Why are you yelling at me?

161
00:08:03,560 --> 00:08:03,959
By the way,

162
00:08:04,639 --> 00:08:05,759
that guy,

163
00:08:06,480 --> 00:08:07,519
Yun Fei,

164
00:08:08,639 --> 00:08:10,560
I thought he looked familiar.

165
00:08:11,319 --> 00:08:12,279
Then I remembered.

166
00:08:12,399 --> 00:08:12,800
He's

167
00:08:12,879 --> 00:08:14,399
your ex-boyfriend, isn't he?

168
00:08:15,079 --> 00:08:15,759
I remember

169
00:08:16,279 --> 00:08:17,600
he works for the government.

170
00:08:17,720 --> 00:08:19,319
Now he's your family.

171
00:08:19,560 --> 00:08:21,240
It's really hard to avoid disasters.

172
00:08:22,959 --> 00:08:24,839
I feel sorry for his future.

173
00:08:25,160 --> 00:08:25,680
You see,

174
00:08:26,000 --> 00:08:28,160
if he gets involved in something shady,

175
00:08:28,680 --> 00:08:29,360
how will he

176
00:08:30,000 --> 00:08:30,879
hold his head up in the future?

177
00:08:31,199 --> 00:08:31,959
To make a long story short,

178
00:08:32,480 --> 00:08:33,639
I can gather the 500,000.

179
00:08:33,679 --> 00:08:34,600
I have only one request:

180
00:08:35,240 --> 00:08:36,039
I want to meet his family.

181
00:08:37,240 --> 00:08:37,960
Listen,

182
00:08:38,440 --> 00:08:39,399
I can give you the money,

183
00:08:39,559 --> 00:08:40,440
or I can give it to them.

184
00:08:40,840 --> 00:08:42,519
I can find them myself if I want to.

185
00:08:42,799 --> 00:08:43,759
If I find them,

186
00:08:44,639 --> 00:08:45,879
will you still get your share?

187
00:08:46,039 --> 00:08:46,960
If you take me to them,

188
00:08:47,759 --> 00:08:49,279
I'll make sure you get your cut.

189
00:08:50,320 --> 00:08:51,039
Otherwise,

190
00:08:51,720 --> 00:08:52,960
you'll be begging on the streets.

191
00:08:54,320 --> 00:08:56,039
You've really crossed the line!

192
00:08:57,720 --> 00:08:58,480
You're nothing!

193
00:09:05,639 --> 00:09:06,159
Hello.

194
00:09:07,399 --> 00:09:08,879
You didn't contact Lan Xiaochuan, did you?

195
00:09:10,279 --> 00:09:11,519
I'm doing this for your own good.

196
00:09:12,080 --> 00:09:13,000
If you contact her,

197
00:09:13,519 --> 00:09:14,799
then our cover will be blown.

198
00:09:15,039 --> 00:09:16,679
How can we ask her for money in the future?

199
00:09:20,279 --> 00:09:21,000
Where are you?

200
00:09:22,960 --> 00:09:24,159
Still at the plaza internet cafe.

201
00:09:24,879 --> 00:09:25,360
Okay, okay.

202
00:09:25,480 --> 00:09:25,960
Good, good.

203
00:09:26,360 --> 00:09:27,559
There's food, drink, and fun there.

204
00:09:27,639 --> 00:09:28,120
Pretty good.

205
00:09:28,879 --> 00:09:29,279
Fine.

206
00:09:30,039 --> 00:09:30,759
You play there.

207
00:09:31,080 --> 00:09:31,960
I'll come to you in a few days.

208
00:09:33,519 --> 00:09:34,440
Okay, okay.

209
00:09:37,440 --> 00:09:38,440
Idiot.

210
00:09:52,679 --> 00:09:53,919
The plaza internet cafe.

211
00:09:54,600 --> 00:09:55,679
Turns out to be hiding there.

212
00:10:30,679 --> 00:10:31,399
Beauty.

213
00:10:32,039 --> 00:10:33,080
You've been with us all the way.

214
00:10:33,279 --> 00:10:34,080
What do you mean?

215
00:10:37,679 --> 00:10:38,240
Liu.

216
00:10:39,399 --> 00:10:40,279
Don't you remember me?

217
00:10:42,720 --> 00:10:43,840
It's you!

218
00:10:45,120 --> 00:10:45,879
What do you want from me?

219
00:10:46,639 --> 00:10:47,600
I'm here to talk about money.

220
00:10:48,440 --> 00:10:49,320
Didn't you want money?

221
00:10:49,720 --> 00:10:50,480
I'll give you money.

222
00:10:50,879 --> 00:10:51,320
Give me all the reports

223
00:10:51,440 --> 00:10:53,279
of your wife from the maternity hospital.

224
00:10:53,960 --> 00:10:54,519
Ultrasound reports,

225
00:10:54,840 --> 00:10:55,840
progesterone test results,

226
00:10:56,039 --> 00:10:57,960
and any documents proving the fetus's condition.

227
00:10:58,279 --> 00:10:59,440
You still have the nerve to ask?

228
00:10:59,759 --> 00:11:01,200
Haven't I already told you?

229
00:11:01,559 --> 00:11:02,399
I burned all those documents

230
00:11:02,559 --> 00:11:03,840
when I performed a ritual

231
00:11:04,039 --> 00:11:04,919
for my child.

232
00:11:05,320 --> 00:11:05,799
You have no evidence.

233
00:11:05,879 --> 00:11:07,600
How can you prove the miscarriage was my fault?

234
00:11:08,279 --> 00:11:09,919
I used the outer gate acupoint on her wrist.

235
00:11:10,240 --> 00:11:11,080
How could it

236
00:11:11,519 --> 00:11:12,759
cause a miscarriage?

237
00:11:12,960 --> 00:11:14,840
You killed my child and you're still lying.

238
00:11:15,039 --> 00:11:16,759
I don't understand your traditional Chinese medicine.

239
00:11:16,960 --> 00:11:17,919
When you stuck that needle in,

240
00:11:18,039 --> 00:11:19,600
did some bad energy go into her belly

241
00:11:19,799 --> 00:11:20,960
and killed my son?

242
00:11:21,240 --> 00:11:22,240
You're just making things up.

243
00:11:22,440 --> 00:11:23,639
You're the one making things up!

244
00:11:23,879 --> 00:11:25,200
Do you know the law?

245
00:11:25,360 --> 00:11:26,360
You killed my son

246
00:11:26,519 --> 00:11:27,519
with your acupuncture.

247
00:11:27,679 --> 00:11:28,720
You killed him!

248
00:11:28,919 --> 00:11:29,600
I'm telling you,

249
00:11:29,879 --> 00:11:32,159
you could be in prison for over a decade.

250
00:11:32,320 --> 00:11:34,159
I'm giving you a chance to repent,

251
00:11:34,399 --> 00:11:36,200
and it's only because of my kindness

252
00:11:36,279 --> 00:11:37,600
that I'm settling this privately.

253
00:11:37,799 --> 00:11:39,000
I'm saving you here.

254
00:11:39,240 --> 00:11:40,639
Do you understand?

255
00:11:44,080 --> 00:11:44,519
Put it down.
